{"tid":2137884,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《頭條動新聞》Ep.1  (蘋果日報 Appledaily)","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T05:17:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1630c25ee705549f7b3f7904d193fd64e06cf8","tid":2137884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"#王喜 #頭條動新聞 #Appledaily<br />\n<br />\n《頭條動新聞》Ep.1 <br />\n(蘋果日報 Appledaily)<br />\nAug 3, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QfHyCq45j4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6QfHyCq45j4&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=fbae4b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QfHyCq45j4</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.68M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n面對強權打壓，批判政府的聲音越來越少，《頭條動新聞》請來《四點鐘王Sir》主持王喜，以及《AppleDaily Show豪》主持曾志豪，繼續與香港人一同嬉笑怒罵、諷刺時弊。如你想支持《頭條動新聞》兩位創作人曾志豪和王喜，可於YouTube收看節目直播期間，按留言位右邊的按鈕，選擇購買「Super Sticker」，或以自由定價的「超級即時通訊」作支持。扣除成本後將全數撥歸合作夥伴，與你攜手撐同路人！<br />\n<br />\n  《四點鐘王Sir》  <br />\n過去一年防暴警執勤其間多次「仆街」，王Sir從裝備上及心理上以至身理上的狀況，詳細解構總總成因，以及在《警察通例》下如何可作出糾正。<br />\n<br />\n《AppleDaily Show豪》<br />\n市民踎街食飯一日後撤回堂食禁令，撤回速度遠勝5個月才願意收回「逃犯條例」，除撤回速度快，DQ速度更快，一連串立會參選人被DQ後，林鄭更將整個選舉徹底DQ，原來《基本法》已成為宗教。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=441eea72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0f107dfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=dc8d7aba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=22fe7377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android</a>"},{"pid":"988783eebaf57be56f70a16640868b1abb02def2","tid":2137884,"uid":92052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a88ef413030e1450a51758fb35c67dde8e5e9fc","tid":2137884,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e2d3966a2aae283c603c25d66699b7bd1f2f52","tid":2137884,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}